title: Speed of Zeit 8/3: Back the Blue, I'll Be Gone in the Dark, The Rock, Bryan Callen, NBA Bubble
itunes:title: Speed of Zeit 8/3: Back the Blue, I'll Be Gone in the Dark, The Rock, Bryan Callen, NBA Bubble
description:
On this edition of Speed of Zeit Jack and Miles discuss the Back the Blue "mural" showing up in Tampa, the HBO series is coming to a close, The Rock bought the XLF for $15 Million, Bryan Callen has been accused of sexual assault by multiple women, and Jack and Miles discuss basketball.
